{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were taken around the streets of our city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there were people standing on the sidewalks, and I think some of them in horror, looking at this scenario.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when we finally moved down on the street, there was a whisper among us, that only was a rumor we couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the direction that this march took, it looked like we were going to our synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And little by little, we got close enough that we could smell the burn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we were taken around our burning synagogue, marched around the burning synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the SS-- or the SR, whoever it was-- had taken a Torah roll out and rolled it out on the street and made us march across the Torah rolls.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were then taken-- after this march de triomphe, we were taken back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we were split up because we were too many to be taken to one prison.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were taken to two different prisons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "In the middle of the next night, we were loaded on open trucks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was still with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, there's another, if I can-- but my-- so we went to-- we were loaded on open trucks and taken in the November night.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of them in-- only in their pajamas with an overcoat over it, without being dressed properly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were taken [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] away from Hildesheim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were going to Hanover.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Hanover, there was a special train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were loaded on the special train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on this special train were Jews from surrounding villages near Hanover, among them from Pattensen, the birthplace of my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
